title: Patriotic Europeans Against islamization of the West
description: The Identitarian Movement began in France in 2003 as Generation Identitaire and spread to Germany as Identitäre Bewegung and to Austria as Identitäre Bewegung Österreichs. Loosely based on the views of 1960's political activist Nouvelle Droite, Identitare is a conservative youth political organization that opposes mass immigration as it's main concern. Identitare groups are composed of citizens of all ages, not just youth. The media and political left smear and libel Identitare as Fascist, Racist and islamophobic. All branches of Identitare merely point to the staggering increase in violent crime and the drained financial and material resources caused by self claimed refugees as reason for grave concern and action. PEGIDA (acronym) is Patriotic Europeans Against the islamization of Deutschland and Austria All videos have quality English subtitles for German speech and most of the text and banners. All 15 videos have the same specs as follows.
